Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.35,Main Dialogue,Dad,0,0,0,,Bạn mày đến rồi kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:29.28,Main Dialogue,Souma,0,0,0,,Ờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.20,Main Dialogue,Souma,0,0,0,,Nào, chiến thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.05,Main Dialogue,Dad,0,0,0,,Xin mời thưởng thức!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:52.26,Main Dialogue,Souma,0,0,0,,Mời dùng thử!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:54.22,Main Dialogue,Mayumi,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:57.62,Main Dialogue,Kid,0,0,0,,Đấu rồi kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:01:00.90,Main Dialogue,Kid,0,0,0,,Trọng tài hôm nay là Mayumi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.48,0:01:14.93,Main Dialogue,Kid,0,0,0,,Cậu có nghĩ là…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:15.90,Main Dialogue,Kid,0,0,0,,…hôm nay cậu ấy sẽ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:18.50,Main Dialogue,Aki,0,0,0,,Suỵt! Mayu đang suy nghĩ mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.50,Main Dialogue,Mayumi,0,0,0,,Bên đây thắng!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:26.57,Main Dialogue,Kid,0,0,0,,Có quyết định rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:29.47,Main Dialogue,Kid,0,0,0,,Hôm nay lão già lại thắng!
